data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home in Clayton County! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom single-family residence is nestled in a serene cul-de-sac, offering both privacy and convenience. With spacious interiors, entering a sweeping owners suite with tray ceilings throughout the house, and in a  prime location. Enjoy the epitome of suburban living with access to a community pool, perfect for leisurely afternoons.This property is a must-see for those seeking comfort and a warm family feel. Don't miss out on this rare opportunity - schedule your showing today!
